{"tid":127233,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"召集隊Band/Busking Team散的原因","createTime":"2017-02-20T03:08:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-24T02:21:43.000Z","uid":80383,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7ad7835996c8ffba2755a5a40b49680ee29590a1","tid":127233,"uid":80383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T03:08:33.000Z","msg":"話說大學玩過下band同出過去busking..<br />\n我就玩keyboard既...由於有一個結他手成鬼日absent又講大話 (約定左逄星期五定唔知六夾既，跟住有個星期話自己要返學做project但係ig post左去旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ) 跟住另一個結他手又成日要話等齊人先夾or出，又係成班唔知可以做咩浪費時間，最後當然不歡而散...<br />\n<br />\n呢排另一個friend有隊team玩開busking，夾得好地地，玩左半年個結他手又一句話逄星期唔知幾都唔再得閒，以後都夾唔到就消失左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 家下搞到佢地企晒係度都唔知點好...唔知係邊度搵結他手返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 就算搵到又要從頭夾過咁<br />\n<br />\n成日都係結他手咁既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"721e42c1915114ee6cf213fefa8fe1b68419ace2","tid":127233,"uid":27256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T08:59:13.000Z","msg":"因為結他多人學姐"},{"pid":"14898c811809d84fcc09221f76dcffc709d1a02e","tid":127233,"uid":80383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T11:26:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為結他多人學姐</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但我同fd個隊都揾唔到replacement <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f389d99534c3c3322769d8d76f3b7264c057898","tid":127233,"uid":33781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T12:31:41.000Z","msg":"初學受唔受"},{"pid":"3d0d87f7046d7b7a9fb6e272b129368cf281cdc7","tid":127233,"uid":80383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T15:10:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>初學受唔受</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n初學? 定幾個月就想夾BAND/出BUSKING???<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b81b44175ec1ae63858d3860f691187bd3e59f7","tid":127233,"uid":67284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T15:12:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>初學受唔受</blockquote><br />\n初學咪岀嚟害人 練好基本功先啦"},{"pid":"54a4ad5c4ab873dcec9793863a0f0a1bd4783047","tid":127233,"uid":80383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T15:29:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>初學受唔受</blockquote><br />\n初學咪岀嚟害人 練好基本功先啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都打左個突............."},{"pid":"4c937690df67abc9f346df48e14d2942bb4d60f3","tid":127233,"uid":1539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T03:53:46.000Z","msg":"想聽下你地平時玩開咩 有無錄音聽下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f1e373b7e16fe2e308577b01a611973a5d6ebbb","tid":127233,"uid":80383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T04:18:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想聽下你地平時玩開咩 有無錄音聽下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我個隊散左3年啦<br />\n你想玩我個fd個隊???<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10f4e01a0dd753a95aae2e2179d0e78b5535baa1","tid":127233,"uid":19145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T07:25:46.000Z","msg":"講你有無心架姐 無就梗係收皮啦"},{"pid":"f05f2ccc20850a99cca9efb325f98f3da3e91cb5","tid":127233,"uid":80383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T08:26:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講你有無心架姐 無就梗係收皮啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但總有一個無咁有心 搞到齊唔到人練 <br />\n😂😂😂😂😂😋😋"},{"pid":"5d90a0ad35ded536089c605af5b830c696e95474","tid":127233,"